dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Ah, this corridor must be the last. Once we're past here, we'll reach the edge of the facility.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: After I retrieve my precious items from there, I'll give you the ownership of the Golden Bough as promised.
Feels like this is gonna end on a rotten note, you gonna be okay with that? Those terrorists really must've run off, seeing how none of 'em showed up...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: It was part of the contract to reclaim the laboratory.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: That's why I kept telling you, Mr. Dongrang. When you draft a contract, you have to be meticulous and calculating, and write it in a way that favors us.
<...Let's get going.>
Fortunately, I didn't see any killing machines here.
However, a couple of unwelcome figures appeared in front of us.
Be on guard, Executive Manager! Someone is ahead of us.
<Yeah, but they aren't holding any weapons...>
They may be unarmed, but you are an incredibly weak and fragile civilian, Executive Manager!
<...Um, thanks? Outis?>

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: Can't you count? You clearly outnumber us by a huge margin. Don't be a baby...

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: Here at last, worms?
It's the same voice that played from the machines. And... it's the same face we saw earlier.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Where are your other members, Senior Researcher Ran?

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: ...You managed to bring more help in that mess, I see.

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: And put away that "senior" crap, we haven't even known each other for long. Don't you see what's going on?

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: They've all evacuated. And here I am... buying time for them.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: That's interesting... We thought we stormed in unexpectedly, yet you knew it in advance and escaped?

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: 'Cause you're worms. Look at you, getting all cocky after receiving the best employee award...

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: Raiding here, dare trying to catch us.
You've got a big mouth. You think you're better than us?
You're outnumbered like you said. That noggin of yours probably knows you'd better surrender, eh?

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: ...Let's say I do. It's clear what you'll do with me.

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: You'll neutralize me and keep me barely alive...

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: "Curing" me with your flaunted regeneration ampules...

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: Rinse and repeat, until you get the answers you want.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Sounds like a problem that can be prevented by giving us the answers right away. Am I asking too much?

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: 'Course you are. Unlike you...

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: We aren't planning to live like roaches that feed on whatever is provided from above.
...This is really getting on my nerves.

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: Ah, whatever~ I've had enough of toying with you.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: What are you trying to...

dataList.title: Technology Liberation Alliance
dataList.content: That's right, show your curiosity only to what's happening immediately before your eyes. That's how a researcher should be.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: Ran...
With an ear-piercing noise, the building was engulfed in an explosion.
All that remains is a charred stain.
<Ngh... That hurt a lot.>

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Are you alright, Mr. Dongrang?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: I'm fine... Someone in Dante's party pushed me away as soon as the blast was heard. You know, the quiet fellow with intimidating eyes.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: I was going to do the same, but I was standing too far away.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Whew, that was close.
After taking the impact for others, Don Quixote and Meursault had been flung all the way to columns supporting the building, their backbones fully exposed.
...Don Quixote in particular was impaled on a pillar.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: It must be the faith that they will come back to life at any time that prompted them to jump into danger without hesitation.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Not out of any sort of friendship or affinity... Isn't that right?
Don Quixote couldn't give any answers, whether due to death or the pointed edge stabbing through her mouth.
...Cough.
<Meursault? You were alive...?>
...It was my directive to protect the manager and see that the company's mission is accomplished.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: That... must be it, yes.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: How convenient. You can recover your body without using regeneration ampules.
<I dunno, the ampule looks handier...>

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Right, is Ms. Shrenne alright? And the other Fixers?

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: We're perfectly sound.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: Your group blocked the blast for us, so we turned out fine.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: That's... why you haven't been taking the ampules. That clock had special powers.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Indeed. After all, I recruited them after thorough screening and testing.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: I see... Well, darn... All the ampules I brought... are useless now.
For some reason, Shrenne lets out a defeated laugh and drops the ampules in her bag to the floor.
It's true... For them—looking at it from a perspective that excludes me—this is certainly a convenient power.
Fatal consequences can be reversed, and the only price is me having to bear the pain.
No, wait.
Is this really fine?
And where does this all this time to rewind come from?
Clock...face... Stop...dawdling about... That yellow-haired lass is dying...
Thoroughly ravaged by the blast, Heathcliff pointed at Don Quixote.
Hurry up and turn it... This... hurts an awful lot...
<...On it.>
